From c514858a4d63ad31351259c015181c9879e996e4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andrew Udvare <audvare@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Feb 2026 00:21:21 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 07/23] Use system glslang (USE_SYSTEM_GLSLANG)

- third_party/CMakeLists.txt: link glslang::SPIRV / glslang::glslang from the
  system CMake package when USE_SYSTEM_GLSLANG is set, else build the bundled
  SPIR-V subset.
- src/xenia/base/glslang_include.h: new wrapper selecting <glslang/SPIRV/...>
  headers when XENIA_USE_SYSTEM_GLSLANG is defined.
- Replace direct third_party/glslang includes in the GPU/SPIR-V translator.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
---
 src/xenia/base/glslang_include.h              | 15 ++++++++++
 src/xenia/gpu/shader_compiler_main.cc         |  2 +-
 src/xenia/gpu/spirv_builder.h                 |  2 +-
